    <item>
      <title>特朗普重返白宫，与新盟友和新目标并驾齐驱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/emboldened-trump-returns-to-power-with-new-allies-clear-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普周一宣誓就职，这仅是美国历史上第二位总统失去职位后成功重返权力——这次回归巩固了他在共和党内作为持久的变革人物而非昙花一现的人物的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/emboldened-trump-returns-to-power-with-new-allies-clear-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾逮捕中国间谍嫌疑人，紧张局势加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/philippines-arrests-suspected-chinese-spy-heating-up-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾官员周一称，菲律宾当局逮捕了一名中国公民和两名菲律宾同伙，罪名是涉嫌间谍活动。此案发生在两国地缘政治紧张局势持续加剧的背景下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/philippines-arrests-suspected-chinese-spy-heating-up-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 09:59:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港首席法官承认在紧张局势下很难聘请海外人才</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/hk-chief-justice-admits-difficulty-hiring-overseas-amid-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港最高法院首席法官表示，地缘政治紧张局势阻碍了法院聘用海外法官的能力，而海外法官的存在对于外国公司来说是一个卖点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/hk-chief-justice-admits-difficulty-hiring-overseas-amid-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 09:34:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
